      "content": "idk im just really busy with work right now and an urgent care trip sounds like such a hassle. if i just keep it elevated and use a compression wrap, do you think it'll probably just be a bad sprain? i'd rather just manage the pain at home for a bit and see if the swelling goes down before i commit to going to a doctor.",
